<p class="mb-4">Undetectable.ai remains a market leader in 2026. It’s built for one purpose: to transform AI text into human text that passes the toughest checks.</p>
<p class="mb-4">*   <strong>How it Works:</strong> You paste your AI-generated text, select your target audience (e.g., "General," "Academic," "Marketing"), and hit humanize. It rewrites content with advanced paraphrasing, alters sentence structures, and introduces strategic "imperfections."
<p class="mb-4">*   <strong>Key Features:</strong>
